    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @pixelastic thanks for your feedback. Your bug actually raised a lot of questions on our side. Since we are working on the new major version of InstantSearch.js, we're exploring a new API that could also contain the ability to change the condition that hides the widgets.\r\n\r\nIn the mean time, shipping your own widget is probably the most straightforward.",
