    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can now achieve this behavior with the [`panel`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/panel/js/) widget in InstantSearch.js 3:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst pagination = instantsearch.widgets.panel({\r\n  hidden: ({ results }) => results.nbPages === 1,\r\n})(instantsearch.widgets.pagination);\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  pagination({\r\n    container: '#pagination',\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2019-03-14T16:35:28Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2992#issuecomment-472952288",
    "id": 472952288,
